item.title: WHY US?
item.description: We wish to become a student body that will address the grievances of our fellow students and strive to find the best solutions for them. We vow to fulfill all the duties and responsibilities assigned to us to the best of our abilities. We promote the ideals of togetherness and seeks to create a great campus experience for each one of you. So, join us in this venture by extending your supporting hand.
